ActTerritorial Lands Act
SubjectWithdrawal from Disposal of Certain Tracts of Territorial Lands in the Northwest Territories (Dehcho First Nations) Order
PrecisWITHDRAWAL FROM DISPOSAL OF CERTAIN TRACTS OF TERRITORIAL LANDS IN THE NORTHWEST TERRITORIES (DEHCHO FIRST NATIONS) ORDER - which withdraws from disposal the surface and subsurface rights of certain lands (approximately 76,367 square kilometers), in order to facilitate the settlement of the Dehcho First Nations Final Agreement for the period beginning on November 1, 2010 and ending October 31, 2011.
